<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="shame-n">shame <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ʃeɪm/    美 /ʃeɪm/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-u">1.★ <strong>[U] 羞耻 (心)；羞愧 (感)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The boy <strong>hung his head in shame</strong>.
那个男孩子羞愧地低下了头。</p></div>

<h4 id="2-pity">2.★ <strong>[常用单数] 可耻的事或人；遗憾的事 (pity)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>It is a shame to</strong> be so wasteful.
这样浪费太可耻了。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>It’s a shame that</strong> you have to leave so soon.
你这么快就要走，真令人遗憾。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="put-to-shame">put … to shame</h3>
<p>1.<strong>大大胜过；使自愧不如</strong><br />
to be much better than sb / sth：</p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>His cooking puts mine to shame.
他的厨艺让我自愧不如。</p></div>

<h3 id="to-sbs-shame">to sb’s shame</h3>
<p>1.<strong>令某人感到羞愧的是：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>To my shame, I made many mistakes because of carelessness.
让我感到羞愧的是，由于粗心我犯了很多错误。</p></div>

<h3 id="what-a-shame">What a shame!</h3>
<p>1.<strong>真遗憾！</strong>  </p>
<h2 id="_3">派生词汇</h2>
<p>shameful /'ʃeɪmfl/ adj <br />
shameless /'ʃeɪmləs/ adj   </p></div>